== How can I install it ?

In the Eclipse Update Site browser, just add the following URL: http://eclipse.worldline.com/nightly/asciidoctools/ for nightly updates and http://eclipse.worldline.com/releases/asciidoctools/0.1.0/ for the first release.

It will give you access to the installer of the Eclipse plugin, as shown on the picture below

